{"tid":1702551,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【內含文宣圖】教你如何用裝修攬炒中共經濟！終極裝修中資攻略Vol.2！","createTime":"2019-11-09T17:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T08:05:58.000Z","uid":64981,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1b2e65b340d374cf4f966f34bcd137416685ee","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"想申請裝修咪直接講囉衰鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GLt6im.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GLt6im.png&h=480c3b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>裝修心法：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">取易不取難</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">先中資</span>，<span style=\"color: blue;\">後藍絲</span><br />\n先<ins>零售</ins>，後金融</strong></div></em></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要專門裝修中資？</span></strong></span><br />\n第一，中資企業係中共希望用作穩定香港經濟／金融中心地位嘅手段，早前已經開咗會要求下面啲馬仔要加大喺香港嘅投資額。而如果要呢一招失敗，<strong>我地就要令中資企業連生意都做唔到！</strong><br />\n<br />\n第二，中共經濟已經越黎越差（人口急劇老化、重工業反噬等等問題，有興趣可以自己查），而中資企業甚或國企，無疑係支撐起中共經濟嘅重要基石。<strong>如果專門裝修中資，就可以將時間集中喺攻擊中共經濟身上，分分鐘喺呢個大環境下，可以成為壓倒中共經濟嘅最後一根稻草！</strong><br />\n<br />\n第三，在港中資本來就係滲透香港嘅方法之一，既然大家要拓展黃絲經濟圈，就好應該出手抗擊所有中資企業喺日常生活嘅生意。當中資店舖做唔到生意，市民就會轉移到其他無咁藍甚至係黃嘅商店，<strong>令香港市民對中資企業嘅依賴逐步減少。</strong><br />\n<br />\n唔係話手足唔應該裝修其他藍店，而係裝修係有風險，可能畀狗咬。既然係咁，點解唔更有戰略咁，集中裝修中資企業、嘗試槓桿出更大回報呢？要記住，我地出黎打嘅目標係光復香港，而唔係發洩，<strong>負擔風險，應該要預期回報；而令中資受損、令中共收入來源受損，就係實質回報。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1eCe9R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1eCe9R.png&h=f4a24fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n=========================<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下為3個中資企業超重心推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 華潤</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKhDJPX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKhDJPX.png&h=53f30992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>華潤貴為四大在港中資企業之一，零售業務廣泛，包括：</strong><br />\nPacific Coffee（咖啡店）<br />\nV&gt;nGO（便利店）<br />\n華潤堂（個人護理店）<br />\nU購Select、華潤萬家（超市）<br />\n中藝（專賣貴價貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>除咗以上商鋪，以下產品都希望大家杯葛：</strong><br />\n雪花、金威、藍劍啤酒（咁多選擇都唔會揀中國貨啦）<br />\n五豐行豬肉（佢自動爆唔洗裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n華潤醫藥（阿膠之類變態藥材）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 中旅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6Q2rcB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6Q2rcB.png&h=d66dae19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中旅都係四大在港中資企業之一，而且由國務院持有，<strong>商鋪主要有分社同辦事處</strong>；<br />\n有一個大家可能唔知，<strong>就係佢地已經收購咗安信兄弟百分之55股權</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 中國相關銀行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5m6MS2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5m6MS2e.png&h=62ae90f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個唔洗講啦，見到「中國」兩個字就幫襯啦，純粹列舉幾個大家未必耳熟能詳嘅中資銀行畀大家認識；不過正如開頭所講，金融類嘅中資企業係比較次要，<strong>如果眼前有一間中銀、一間Pacific，衝入去Pacific先</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於中資銀行而言，最重要都係呼籲大家停用、杯葛，老豆老母一定要勸，甚至直頭要出文宣，呼籲大家儘快提款，話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暴徒瘋狂破壞中資銀行，存款恐怕不保</span></strong>就最好喇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Honorable mention：</span></span><br />\n三、中、商（書局）<br />\n名創優品（支那）<br />\n蘇寧電器（支那）<br />\n康泰旅行社（海航持有過半股份）<br />\n=========================<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武運亨通，光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"153ab412b5c25bb779c87834a30a83eb1facf8cc","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:52:22.000Z","msg":"如果大家有中資企業，而有方便大家裝修嘅都可以講<br />\n<br />\n最緊要取易不取難"},{"pid":"93b2822855a7b6a74b71ebe8bb6afb22bda16270","tid":1702551,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"07ea9f1121931ad08b465b24f6f2d536e9707187","tid":1702551,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"巴打啲圖好shareable<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f656ca3056de529d00a476b07336dd2f54f0b83","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae32bc88a90fa2d201fc5524e04d590da3385c09","tid":1702551,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78da6b5d85c0bdbcd6492d6320746e089df571d8","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae32bc88a90fa2d201fc5524e04d590da3385c09","tid":1702551,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee86d6984d3e37d8df04bd7cd5bccf8f5cfaa8c","tid":1702551,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家只係叫你早D起身出門支持聲援，同埋唔好如常返返公司個位當無事發生過，咁都做唔到，香港人真係唔配有公義、民主同自由。。。。。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re09Mt0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre09Mt0.jpg&h=49aba454&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9Pq4fG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9Pq4fG.jpg&h=02c729ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5ed56e75b21a3466179813e48780da6793680b8","tid":1702551,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"所有有份推送中同禁幪面法嘅行會成員<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">張宇人<br />\n太興、大家樂</span></span>"},{"pid":"723920991b6cdbccf29001f27909c1626d19ecda","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"不過其實裝修乜舖頭，都係會有動亂效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b07a92c8ff47e07412d8e0e140c5eee84e5879","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ed56e75b21a3466179813e48780da6793680b8","tid":1702551,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"所有有份推送中同禁幪面法嘅行會成員<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">張宇人<br />\n太興、大家樂</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"太興抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc7cba4551e47c8fb2bedc95c020345ca078469","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"呢個post啲圖靚啲<br />\n大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a43ff842b3e66ab82f1c67f794b1cdbcb31388c","tid":1702551,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"【內含文宣圖】教你如何用裝修攬炒中共經濟！終極裝修中資攻略Vol.2！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702551</a>"},{"pid":"f471